=> Create the functions file and save it. Only functions should be included.

=> Use "source /path/to/file.sh" to import the file to the script.

=> Then use the function name to call it inside the script.

=> External file (message_file.sh):
  display_message(){
    echo "Hello"
  }
=> Script file:
      #!/bin/bash
      source message_file.sh

      display_message
  // This file will output "Hello"
